product.summary: Office suite integrated into your own infrastructure
A powerful online editor for ECM

overview.overview: Collabora Online is a powerful collaborative Office suite that supports all major document, spreadsheet and presentation file formats, which you can integrate into your own infrastructure.

highlights: Integrated with Nextcloud, ownCloud by default

childMarkdownRemark.html: Collabora Online provides data security and sovereignty, and is ideally suited to the demands of a modern distributed working environment. Delivering a familiar look and feel, Collabora Online represents a real alternative to other big-brands solutions, giving you control and flexibility.
